this is a sign for you and your best to go do Bombay Darshan! 

your itinerary can be- 

1- start off by picking up an amazing cold coffee or match from @mumbaiblondie ☕️
2- Head to Khar Station get a local 🚃 for all the vibes and the heat 🚂
3- Get off at Churchgate take a Kaali Peeli and go to @kgafest 🎨🖼️
4- Walk to @colaba_causeway and shop till you drop don’t forget to bargain 🛍️
5- Head to @leopoldcafemumbai to fuel up 🍻
6- End the night opposite @tajmahalmumbai ⛵️ 
7- Go back home in a Kaali Peeli through @coastal.road @sea_link 🚖
